<li>1994 <a href="/wiki/Minette_Walters" title="Minette Walters">Minette Walters</a>, <i><a href="/wiki/The_Sculptress" title="The Sculptress">The Sculptress</a></i></li>
<li>1993 <a href="/wiki/Margaret_Maron" title="Margaret Maron">Margaret Maron</a>, <i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Bootlegger%27s_Daughter&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Bootlegger's Daughter (page does not exist)">Bootlegger's Daughter</a></i></li>
<li>1992 <a href="/wiki/Lawrence_Block" title="Lawrence Block">Lawrence Block</a>, <i><a href="/w/index.php?title=A_Dance_at_the_Slaughterhouse&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="A Dance at the Slaughterhouse (page does not exist)">A Dance at the Slaughterhouse</a></i></li>
